=== COLLAPSING_STRUCTURE ===
# id: 39
# title: The Collapsing Structure
# chinese_title: 崩塌
# category: Hazard
# mode: dungeon

The ceiling groans ominously and dust rains down as structural supports buckle. A section of the floor ahead has already given way, revealing the deck below. You can hear stressed metal creaking — this whole area could come down any moment.

* [Dash across before it collapses]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "快" (kuài) — fast, quick
* [Reinforce the supports temporarily] {requires: class == 1}
  ~ gain_radical("土")
  "土" (tǔ) — earth, ground, foundation
* [Drop to the lower deck through the hole]
  ~ damage(5)
  "落" (luò) — to fall, to drop
* [Find a structural bypass]
  ~ gain_xp(10)
  "绕" (rào) — to go around, to detour
